xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 22, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104tvq1665702743685.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/tvq1665702743685.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/tvq1665702743685.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"tvq1665702743685\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"tvq1665702743685__testable_481156\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specifies whether the test page (Uniface Test Middleware Response ) can be\n      displayed.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"tvq1665702743685__topic_d147593e1_d147594e1_d147595e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tvq1665702743685__p_d147596e1_d147597e1_d147598e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;init-param&gt;\n &lt;param-name&gt;</code>\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">TESTABLE</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;/param-name&gt;\n &lt;param-value&gt;</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">TRUE</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">FALSE</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;/param-value&gt;\n &lt;/init-param&gt;</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tvq1665702743685__p_d147599e1_d147600e1_d147601e1\">Default value if omitted: <code class=\"ph codeph\">TRUE</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tvq1665702743685__topic_d106407e1_d106408e1_d106409e1_d106410e1_d106411e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d915717e83\">Values</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"tvq1665702743685__li_d51227e1_d51228e1_d51229e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">TRUE</code>—generates the test page containing version information about\n               the current WRD.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"tvq1665702743685__li_d51230e1_d51231e1_d51232e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">FALSE</code>—displays an error page. An activate error <code class=\"ph codeph\">-50</code>\n               is returned, as for any other request for a nonexistent server page.</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tvq1665702743685__topic_d106412e1_d106413e1_d106414e1_d106415e1_d106416e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d915717e107\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tvq1665702743685__p_d147608e1_d147609e1_d147610e1\">You can use this setting when configuring the web server (or servlet engine) to run the WRD, to confirm that the web server is able to connect to Uniface.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tvq1665702743685__p_d147611e1_d147612e1_d147613e1\">Once the WRD is confirmed to be running, you can set <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">TESTABLE</span> to <code class=\"ph codeph\">FALSE</code> or remove it completely, so that the version information is not accessible.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tvq1665702743685__section_wwr_1n1_ddc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d915717e125\">Example: Using TESTABLE</h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">Set <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">TESTABLE</span> to true.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"tvq1665702743685__pre_mmk_bn1_ddc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">&lt;init-param&gt;\n &lt;param-name&gt;TESTABLE&lt;/param-name&gt;\n &lt;param-value&gt;true&lt;/param-value&gt;\n&lt;/init-param&gt;</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">After restarting the web server (to pick up the new value of the\n               setting), enter the URL for the test page:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"tvq1665702743685__ul_pmk_bn1_ddc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"tvq1665702743685__li_d51233e1_d51234e1_d51235e1\">If the servlet setting\n                     <code class=\"ph codeph\">USERUNPREFIX</code> is <code class=\"ph codeph\">false</code>:\n                        <code class=\"ph codeph\">http://<var class=\"keyword varname\">ServerHost</var>/uniface/wrd/WRD_Version</code>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"tvq1665702743685__li_d51236e1_d51237e1_d51238e1\">If the servlet setting\n                     <code class=\"ph codeph\">USERUNPREFIX</code> is <code class=\"ph codeph\">true</code>:\n                        <code class=\"ph codeph\">http://<var class=\"keyword varname\">ServerHost</var>/uniface/wrd/run/WRD_Version</code>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"tvq1665702743685__fig_w2556ab1b5b7b7c11_w2557ab1b5b7b7_w2558ab1b5b7_w2559ab1b5_w2560ab1\"><figcaption><span class=\"fig--title-label\">Figure 1. </span>Uniface Test Middleware Response Page</figcaption>\n<img alt=\"Uniface Test Middleware Response Page\" class=\"image\" id=\"tvq1665702743685__image_rgk_2j3_rcc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/Uniface-Test-Server-Page.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yda1665702742322.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>web.xml</a><p>Configuration file of the web application.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/uhg1665702743762.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>UseRunPrefix</a><p>Specifies whether the WRD should handle references to documents on relative paths (such as ../css/applic.css).</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532542\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532542\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "TESTABLE Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 22, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Specifies whether the test page (Uniface Test Middleware Response ) can be displayed. <init-param> <param-name> TESTABLE </param-name> <param-value> TRUE | FALSE </param-value> </init-param> Default value if omitted: TRUE Values TRUE —generates the test page containing version information about the current WRD. FALSE —displays an error page. An activate error -50 is returned, as for any other request for a nonexistent server page. Description You can use this setting when configuring the web server (or servlet engine) to run the WRD, to confirm that the web server is able to connect to Uniface. Once the WRD is confirmed to be running, you can set TESTABLE to FALSE or remove it completely, so that the version information is not accessible. Example: Using TESTABLE Set TESTABLE to true. <init-param> <param-name>TESTABLE</param-name> <param-value>true</param-value> </init-param> Copy After restarting the web server (to pick up the new value of the setting), enter the URL for the test page: If the servlet setting USERUNPREFIX is false : http:// ServerHost /uniface/wrd/WRD_Version If the servlet setting USERUNPREFIX is true : http:// ServerHost /uniface/wrd/run/WRD_Version Figure 1. Uniface Test Middleware Response Page Related Links web.xml Configuration file of the web application. UseRunPrefix Specifies whether the WRD should handle references to documents on relative paths (such as ../css/applic.css). Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}